# Becoming a LADAL contributor{-}

If you have an idea for a tutorial, you can download this [skeleton Rmd](https://slcladal.github.io/content/base.Rmd) and write your own LADAL tutorial. You can then send us the Rmd file (with any additional files we need to knit the document) and we will then check it. Once your tutorial has been approved, it will be published as a proper LADAL tutorial.


